## MULTI-REGIONAL NOTES

* Sector access is filtered by player's current region
* Players in different regions see different sector sets
* Central Nexus sectors accessible from all regions (subject to subscription tier filters)
* Genesis devices can only be deployed in player's current region
* Capital Sector of every region holds the Pioneer Office (Class-0 station) — fixed at sector 1 in Terran Space, randomized within Federation Zone in player regions, anchored in Gateway Plaza cluster of Central Nexus

